    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1915-04-01T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1915-04-01T00:00:00-05:00" n="520"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d520">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 838.00/1154.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Minister
                            <persName type="to">Sullivan</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Santo Domingo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-04-01">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 1, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your March 28. You will support the President in his determination to prevent the
                    use of Dominican territory as a base for hostilities against Haiti. This would
                    be proper under any circumstances, but is the more necessary in view of Bobo’s
                    manifest hostility towards the United States.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bryan</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
